8T19:28:13.000Z","msg":"雞 全部都係雞"},{"pid":"2574707a808487d044e4373a2b72136d67cb058a","tid":2317673,"uid":206185,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"建議lock機, 再望下個mon"},{"pid":"8b5fe14950ebd808126cbc9c3d9ff66218467486","tid":2317673,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e0a667520e8a533db070b38fb569ccaaa9c75157","tid":2317673,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:16:29.000Z","msg":"You"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:37:27.000Z","msg":"Stfu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46763b69034a999cd6bfcb6660df734dd4837eb","tid":2317673,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T20:18:54.000Z","msg":"大把人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf923b7607321e2fc2ec9cada0c0964d4733db8","tid":2317673,"uid":364666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T20:24:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b556dca49b72aae24378575045cd84cc39601dd9","tid":2317673,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T20:44:29.000Z","msg":"大學努力讀書，第時比心機出嚟搵錢，到30幾歲就有女搵你埋單，到時你同條女結婚同層樓落佢名，結婚果晚咪有得扑，急咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a028c5c766d7d965d97c3ba20798b20f1db210","tid":2317673,"uid":316086,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T21:06:46.000Z","msg":"升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你荒（慌）無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達二萬零五百蚊。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過三十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有一萬八千蚊，比自己足足少了二千多元！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」"},{"pid":"93c221d9838f5b55e2b51d7f1093c4a51e1848b0","tid":2317673,"uid":4526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:29:44.000Z","msg":"我去咗建興大廈搵樓主破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f71f31c07d5857c97d29707f5c1a5b80c48f71c","tid":2317673,"uid":306413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4b4390bf807ae94cbd647f9ba936bd76ad9b65f7","tid":2317673,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"5b9e84ed509378d30846b84de587e1358f02db86","tid":2317673,"uid":238769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:09:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪檢討緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"我16歲俾咗隻豬男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"豬乜柒<br />\n咪又係臭hi"},{"pid":"f58ff91a5834dcd33487cca3db63a577761b59d4","tid":2317673,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4390bf807ae94cbd647f9ba936bd76ad9b65f7","tid":2317673,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"5b9e84ed509378d30846b84de587e1358f02db86","tid":2317673,"uid":238769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:09:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪檢討緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"我16歲俾咗隻豬男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"伯母仲勁<br />\n14"}]}